#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:1
msgid "Binary Contraption"
msgstr "二進制裝置"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:23
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:44
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Hello-o-o-o-o-o, Dragon Rider!  It’s great to see your stupid face again.  I’m working on a sick computer-thingy that will power a mechanical walker, the coolest new attack vehicle around!  Bring me some Unobtainium, and I’ll give it to you."
msgstr "你好-嗷，龍騎士！又看到你這張蠢臉了，真不錯。我在做一個超酷的電腦裝置，用來驅動一臺機械步行機甲！給我一些難得素，我就把它送給你。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:24
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:45
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "C’mon, you knew you’d need to do something before I give up the prize.  But hey, I appreciate you going to hell and back for me.  Literally!  Hahaha!"
msgstr "來吧，你知道的，有付出才有回報。但嘿，我感謝你為我下地獄又爬回來一趟。字面意思上的！哈哈哈！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:29
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:50
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have the Unobtainium."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有難得素。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:25
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "Not bad, Dragon Rider.  But I’m gonna need way more Unobtainium than this.  Bring me some more tomorrow, and we’ll see."
msgstr "不錯，龍騎士。但這點難得素遠遠不夠。明天在帶來多一點吧。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Binary%20Contraption.xml:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Oh all right.  I guess this is enough Unobtainium.  Here ya go, Dragon Rider.  But don’t break my computer!  I’ll pop ya one in the nose."
msgstr "好。我想這已經夠了。拿著這個，龍騎士。但別弄壞它！不然我會一拳打你鼻子。"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:1
msgid "Dragon Pants"
msgstr "龍褲"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "That no good stinking Dragon Lord!  I’d like to wring his lordly neck!"
msgstr "那個該死的、臭烘烘的龍主！我要擰斷他那該死的脖子！"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Too much time under ground, too many explosions—let’s be honest, I’m pretty nuts.  But not as nuts as that punk Dragon Lord.  Let’s chew his ankles off!  Or I could help you make stuff to fight him.  That too."
msgstr "在地下停留的時間太長了，爆炸太多了——說實話，我自己也有點不太正常了。但不像那個廢物龍主。乾脆把他腳踝啃下來！或者我也可以幫你做點東西來對付他。這個也行。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "I’ve been thinking, and maybe this is just a crazy conspiracy theory, but I think the angry streak we goblins have is due to the Dragon Lord’s meddling.  Our weak minds were influenced too easily."
msgstr "我一直在想，也許這只是一個瘋狂的陰謀論，但我仍認為我們哥布林的憤怒全在於龍主的干預。我們的腦子太容易被操控了。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have crafted the Dragon Pants."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你已經制作了龍褲。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "You look rather fetching in those pants, Dragon Rider.  Even if the Dragon Lord smashes you with one blow, at least you’ll look stylish being obliterated."
msgstr "你穿那條褲子還挺惹眼的，龍騎士。就算龍主一拳打死你，至少被轟成渣的時候還能看起來挺有型。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:40
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Even I’m not crazy enough to want the Dragon Lord to rule the land.  That guy is a jerk!\n"
"\n"
"There’s just one more piece of dragon gear to go, but you’ll need a master craftsman to make this one.  Maybe that wimpy warrior can help you."
msgstr ""
"我還沒瘋到來希望龍主統治這片土地。那傢伙真是個混蛋！\n"
"\n"
"只剩下一件了，但你得找個熟練點的工匠來製作它。也許那個慫包戰士可以幫幫你。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Dragon%20Pants.xml:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Speak to Aaron about the next piece of dragon gear."
msgstr "與艾倫談談下一件龍防具。"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:1
msgid "Explosive Knowledge"
msgstr "爆炸知識"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "I promised to help you make things go kaboom, so let's start with the basics."
msgstr "我答應過會幫你，所以先從最基礎的來。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:19
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Step one: Make gunpowder.\n"
"\n"
"Step two: Blow stuff up!\n"
"\n"
"Step one is not the fun part, but you gotta start somewhere."
msgstr ""
"先，製作火藥。\n"
"\n"
"再，炸掉東西！\n"
"\n"
"第一步很無聊，但那是必須的。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"I can’t wait to show you how to make TNT.  I can almost smell the sulfur.\n"
"\n"
"But first we are going to need some gunpowder."
msgstr ""
"我真的很想向你展示如何製作炸藥。我幾乎聞到了硫磺味。\n"
"\n"
"但首先我們得要一些火藥。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:35
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have crafted the gunpowder."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你製作了火藥。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "I can’t believe I spent all that time living under a mountain.  Have you been up here this whole time, doing stuff for people?  Dang!"
msgstr "我簡直不敢相信我一直都住在山下。我在那兒的時候你一直都在幫其他人嗎？天啊！"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "With that Gunpowder in hand, making TNT should be a breeze.  It’s fun, too."
msgstr "有了火藥，製作炸藥就很容易，也很好玩。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can never have too much dynaminte.  Trust me, you’ll have a...blast?  Eee hee hee!!!!"
msgstr "炸藥這種東西，永遠不會嫌多。相信我，你會……玩得很“炸”？嘻嘻嘻!!!!"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:74
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have crafted the TNT."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你製作了TNT。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "We’ve got explosives.  KABLAMMO!"
msgstr "我們有炸藥了——轟隆！"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now we can blow things up!  It’s going to be violent and bl-ech, ack!"
msgstr "現在我們能炸掉東西！這肯定很暴力，嘔——呃啊！"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Explosive%20Knowledge.xml:103
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Oh, my little green head.  What happened?  And why do I suddenly have the overwhelming desire to read?\n"
"\n"
"[FF00FF]* shudder *[-]"
msgstr ""
"哦，我這小綠腦袋……發生啥了？為什麼我突然強烈想讀書？\n"
"\n"
"[FF00FF]*顫抖*[-]"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:1
msgid "Goblin Secret"
msgstr "哥布林的秘密"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Is there something I can do for you?  Ah.  That Alchemist fellow told you that I might be able to help you create some armor out of those skins?  Well, I've got good news and bad news."
msgstr "我能幫你些什麼嗎？鍊金術士告訴你，我會幫你用皮毛做盔甲，對吧？好吧，有個好消息，也有個壞消息。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:15
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:29
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Talk to Mr. Goblin about his secrets."
msgstr "與哥布林先生談談他的秘密。"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The good news is that I can definitely show you how to make some armor.\n"
"\n"
"The bad news is that you retrieved the wrong kind of skins."
msgstr ""
"好消息是，我可以向你演示如何製作這些盔甲。\n"
"\n"
"但壞消息是，你拿來的皮毛種類不對。"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "You see.  Goblins like to use horse skins to craft their armor.  We tend to get pretty large and a deer just doesn't cut it."
msgstr "你看，哥布林一般用馬皮製作盔甲，我們的體型比較大，所以鹿皮根本不夠用。"

#. (itstool) path: collectstep/intro
#. (itstool) path: collectstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:48
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you want to learn how to craft the goblin helmet you are going to have to retrieve some horse skins first.  Return to me when you have them."
msgstr "要是想學習怎麼製作哥布林頭盔，你要找些馬皮。然後回到我這兒。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin that you have the horse skins."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有馬皮。"

#. (itstool) path: collectstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:50
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Excellent!  Now you can start looking more like a goblin.\n"
"\n"
"But this is only the beginning.  I require some things to be taken care of around these parts before I'm willing to part with more of my goblin secrets."
msgstr ""
"太棒了！現在你看起來越來越像個哥布林了。\n"
"\n"
"但這只是開始。在我願意告訴你更多哥布林秘密之前，這一帶還有些事情需要你去處理。"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "Goblins tend to have too much meat in our diets.  Now that statement is entirely debatable as some of my goblin friends may not share that sentiment."
msgstr "哥布林的飲食裡通常肉比較多。不過這一點其實還挺有爭議的，因為一些哥布林朋友有不同的意見。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:77
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "I could really use a change of taste.  Bring me some apples and beehives.  I have an idea on how to make one tasty apple."
msgstr "我可以改下口味，給我一些蘋果和蜂巢。我有辦法把一個蘋果變得更”好吃“。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:87
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin that you have the apples and beehives."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有了蘋果和蜂蜜。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:79
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Thank you kind gatherer of ingredients.  Now let's try this out.\n"
"\n"
"Bleh.  Oh my....  This is way too sweet.  I think I'm gonna...\n"
"\n"
"Anyway.  Thanks for giving me a chance to test my theory."
msgstr ""
"謝謝幫忙。現在讓我試一下。\n"
"\n"
"哦，我…這太甜了。我感覺我快要……\n"
"\n"
"總之，謝謝。"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "I wasn't bluffing that I wanted to try something new.  We will just have to try something different entirely."
msgstr "我不是在虛張聲勢，我想試點完全不一樣的東西。那就試試吧。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:109
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "I was thinking.  What do you think about some soup with shark fin in it?  Really?  You already have a recipe for that?  Well then, brew me up some why don't you.  I'm a large guy.  Make me enough to fill my belly."
msgstr "我正在想，要不要來點魚翅湯？真的嗎？你已經有這道菜的食譜了？那為什麼不做點魚翅湯來補補我這個大個子的轆轆飢腸呢？"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:115
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin that you have the shark fin soup."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有魚翅湯。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wow!  That is some truly delicious soup.  Thank you.  Here is the last part of the goblin armor as promised."
msgstr "哇哦！多美味的湯哦！謝謝，這是你盔甲配方的最後一部分。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Goblin%20Secret.xml:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "I wish you luck in your adventures.  Perhaps in time I will require your services again."
msgstr "祝你旅途愉快！或許未來我們還有合作的機會。"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:1
msgid "Pillage Victim"
msgstr "搶劫受害者"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Eee hee hee!  Look who it is.  A Dragon Rider come to chat with little old me?"
msgstr "嘻嘻！看看這是誰。龍騎士要和我聊天嗎？"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Whatever you think I did, I’m innocent, I swear!  $#@!  See?  I swore.  Those goblins that attacked you had nothing to do with me.  They stole my goblin armor.  And now I feel naked without it.  Make me new armor, and I’ll teach you how to make things go kaboom!"
msgstr "不管你覺得我做了些啥，我都是無辜的，我發誓！$#@...！看到了嗎？我發誓了。那些襲擊你的哥布林和我無關。他們偷走了我的盔甲。現在我感覺赤裸裸的。如果你給我些新的盔甲，我就教你怎麼讓一些東西炸掉！"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Ooh, yeah!  You almost got it!\n"
"\n"
"Make me new armor, and I’ll teach you how to make things go kaboom!"
msgstr ""
"哦，是的！你大概知道了！\n"
"\n"
"如果你給我盔甲，我就教你怎麼炸掉東西！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have his replacement goblin armor."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有哥布林盔甲。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Armor!  Oh sweet goblin shell.  Sniff—Blech!  It smells like armpits and sun-dried cheese.  Ah...just like home."
msgstr "盔甲！喔，不錯的哥布林外殼。(嗅)—咳！它聞起來就像曬乾的奶酪。啊...就像家一樣。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "So I was posing in that armor you made me and an acorn fell out of the sky and landed on my head.  War wound!  Now I’ve got a bump.  Fix this problem, Dragon Rider, or I’ll get angry.  And you wouldn’t like me when I’m angry."
msgstr "所以我正穿著你給我的盔甲，而且橡子從天上掉下來落在我的頭上。現在我碰到問題了。解決掉它，龍騎士，不然我會很生氣。你不會喜歡讓我生氣的。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "I got hit on the head so hard I saw stars!  Marilyn Monroe and Clark Gable and even Humphrey Bogart."
msgstr "我的頭受了重擊，看不到星星！我看到了瑪麗蓮夢露，克拉克蓋博，甚至亨佛萊鮑嘉。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Mr. Goblin you have his replacement goblin helmet."
msgstr "告訴哥布林先生，你有哥布林頭盔。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Sweet dome, Dragon Rider!  This helmet is even thicker than my skull, and that’s saying something!"
msgstr "不錯的圓頂帽，龍騎士！這個頭盔比我的頭骨還要厚，這說明了一些東西！"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/MrGoblin/Pillage%20Victim.xml:67
#, no-wrap
